# BRIEF
#! Trivial implementation of sc_main.

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<sc-main template> - Trivial implementation of sc_main.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> sc-main [-d {:I<DIR>:}] {:I<NAME>:}

=head1 DESCRIPTION

      {:NAME:}.cpp -- contains advanced implementation of sc_main

This skeleton is designed to compile out of the box with the OSCI
libraries.

Hint: A better implementation may be found in the template sc-top.

Note: If you want the file to have the conventional name, use the syntax:

    new sc-main main

=head1 PARAMETERS

None

=head1 REQUIREMENTS

Assumes installation of SystemC.

=head1 SEE ALSO

sc-top provides a more sophisticated solution.

